title: Unexpected Error in Mac Client
body: Yesterday everything was normal until I logged out and logged back on League on my Mac. Then there is a box said "unexpected error occurred please check the log file". I tried many different solutions but nothing worked. Any explain or advice? {{item:3073}} {{champion:32}}

replies.body:
Hey there,

Sorry to hear this is happening, could you please attach your latest patcher log file, found in the directory listed below in an email to **oce-wrenchmen@googlegroups.com** Don't forget to include your thread link in the email.

>C:\Riot Games\League of Legends\Logs\Patcher Logs
